<h1 local-id=3D"9d9b1eb32f32" id=3D"Task20-RAD-6.RiskAnalysis">6. Risk Anal=
ysis</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"640d83373489" id=3D"Task20-RAD-6.1RiskIdentification">6.1 R=
isk Identification</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f61d7c1f-2c00-42df-bb9f-31a=
92f235262" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7330e591515c">Risk</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"10ee6d94b52d">Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"94779156e57e">Likelihood</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2d13aa93fec9">Impact</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"31bff58bf07e">DNS propagation delay</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ea9b313a916b">NS record changes may take minutes to hours to=
 propagate globally depending on TTL</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"de41587cee1b">High</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1b77efb5548e">Medium</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3b551f64e37e">Incorrect NS configuration</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5e31e7f23d97">Wrong NS values at the registrar cause domain =
to stop resolving entirely</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3471d0004a44">Medium</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a8b7d0d11de0">High</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"69b76705f4e3">EC2 server downtime</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d41a9e3869b5">BIND9 EC2 instance becomes unreachable =E2=80=
=94 all DNS queries for the zone fail</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"864b89da3aec">Low</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3b58e2e78b30">High</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6b97c755b7cb">Misconfigured DNS records</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"469369930346">Typos in zone file cause resolution failures o=
r incorrect IP mapping</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ad3028167123">Medium</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2dead6c27583">Medium</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"af7e93ce9830">Port 53 blocked</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b5a57d30931f">EC2 Security Group missing port 53 rules cause=
s external queries to time out</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8e78613440ce">Medium</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5f815cb31cd9">High</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"7fa2677efa30" id=3D"Task20-RAD-6.2RiskMitigation">6.2 Risk =
Mitigation</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f5bd808e-03a8-4cab-a17c-f1f=
3d3ac9fed" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2ebe0891008c">Risk</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3d82e976966b">Mitigation</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eb02dc427877">DNS propagation delay</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"12cb602e5449">Set low TTL values (300 seconds) during testin=
g; use dig +trace to monitor live propagation status</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d955eaa26109">Incorrect NS configuration</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6b73a2187c4e">Double-check NS record values against the actu=
al BIND9 EC2 IP and Route 53 NS hostnames before saving</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"65d64e6f201b">EC2 server downtime</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7ffb44f759b2">Configure systemd to auto-restart BIND9 on fai=
lure; maintain Route 53 as an emergency fallback</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"891e2e1f09ed">Misconfigured DNS records</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"70185124e722">Validate all zone file changes with named-chec=
kzone before restarting the service</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f17f2f7be421">Port 53 blocked</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2c0558250ca8">Verify Security Group inbound rules include UD=
P/TCP port 53 before beginning external testing</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"ea4670697c95" id=3D"Task20-RAD-7.Glossary">7. Glossary</h1>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"1c9263a0-0aa6-4c10-906f-135=
0be78ba1c" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bda5c17dafba">Term</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a9f719764bd8">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f9a75765d8d1">DNS Resolution</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"96dec8b32ee0">The process of converting a human-readable dom=
ain name into an IP address by querying the DNS hierarchy</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b417483e73fc">Authoritative Server</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6ee411f1dbe4">The DNS server that holds the definitive recor=
ds for a domain zone and provides the final answer to queries</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"66dbbb42f991">Propagation</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b1d890169569">The time required for DNS changes (NS updates,=
 record modifications) to be reflected across all global resolvers and cach=
ing servers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3dd14fdd205a">Zone File</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"87c18736add2">A text file on the DNS server containing all r=
esource records for a DNS zone =E2=80=94 including SOA, NS, A, and CNAME re=
cords</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1b25513e891b">Glue Record</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cc2e51eaa6dd">An A record provided alongside an NS record to=
 resolve the IP of a nameserver that is within the delegated zone itself</p=
></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dca999cee01f">TTL</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"055e64816907">Time To Live =E2=80=94 the duration in seconds=
 that a DNS response may be cached by resolvers before re-querying</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c8a6632dc62a">SOA Record</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9e08f871a0a2">Start of Authority =E2=80=94 the first record =
in a zone file defining the zone's primary nameserver, admin contact, and s=
erial number</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
